reviewText: This is not helpful tips for barrel racing but just about barrel racing in general. So if your looking for helpful info for training this isn't the one. Although it is informative about life as a barrel racer on the road.
Amazing!!!! Worth the money!! Every barrel racer will love this. I've watched it at least 10 times. My rating is a five!!
I got this for my daughter and she has watched it at least 2 dozen times. She loves it and her times have gotten better.
